Name: Savanna
Description: My name is Savanna. I’ve been a licensed cosmetologist for five years. Although I specialize in fading, I love working with long hair just as much! In September 2019 I opened up Studio Flex. Studio Flex is located inside Chicago sports and fitness club. The Studio Flex team consist of 7 dedicated, motivated, and goal oriented team members each specializing in their own field. Services at Studio Flex are mens and woman’s haircuts and colors, lash extensions, microbladding, facials, nails, waxing, lash lifts/tints and much more! It’s with great pleasure that we can have so much talent in one space. We strive to accommodate our clients in anyway we can. Stop by to book an appointment for any of the services at Studio Flex! Your services is greatly appreciated.
